1
00:01:14,080 --> 00:01:15,640
Gang, no need to see us off.

2
00:01:17,600 --> 00:01:19,120
A couple from our Dayang Village

3
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:20,760
has finally made it out.

4
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,600
You must come visit us.

5
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:23,800
Definitely.

6
00:01:25,440 --> 00:01:26,770
Let's load the luggage.

7
00:01:41,880 --> 00:01:42,920
Take care, Gang.

8
00:01:47,600 --> 00:01:48,400
Gang.

9
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:50,720
Take care.

10
00:01:53,039 --> 00:01:53,570
Let's go.

11
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:55,000
Get in.

12
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,180
Let's go, brother.

13
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,360
Yang Gang.

14
00:03:16,040 --> 00:03:16,960
Jiang Xiaomei.

15
00:03:20,880 --> 00:03:22,210
I thought you were dead.

16
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:24,860
Sit down first.

17
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:36,520
Yes.

18
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:39,640
Xiao Tianman thinks I'm dead.

19
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:41,680
But heaven wouldn't take me.

20
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:44,840
So I'm back for revenge.

21
00:04:23,280 --> 00:04:25,940
Luo Zhengqiang's death and your mother's death

22
00:04:26,200 --> 00:04:28,930
are both connected to Xiao Tianman, aren't they?

23
00:04:31,080 --> 00:04:36,680
So we have a common enemy.

24
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:39,450
What do you want me to do?

25
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:41,960
I have a plan.

26
00:04:42,280 --> 00:04:45,320
We can lure Xiao Tianman into the K26 mine.

27
00:04:59,000 --> 00:04:59,860
President Gao.

28
00:05:04,080 --> 00:05:04,880
Yang Gang.

29
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,570
You dare to show up here?

30
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:10,780
President Gao, calm down.

31
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:12,700
How can I calm down?

32
00:05:13,280 --> 00:05:15,140
I just want to tell you something.

33
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:17,700
You gave the recording pen to Situ Hongtang.

34
00:05:17,840 --> 00:05:19,370
And you still dare to see me?

35
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:34,760
President Gao, please calm down first.

36
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:36,560
The reason I came to you this time

37
00:05:36,840 --> 00:05:40,040
is to give you a chance to take revenge with your own hands.

38
00:05:40,320 --> 00:05:41,159
Do you want it?

39
00:05:42,080 --> 00:05:43,040
What do you mean?

40
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:48,480
I have an appointment with Xiao Tianman to see the gold mine.

41
00:05:49,159 --> 00:05:51,020
I've planted explosives inside.

42
00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:53,159
As soon as Xiao Tianman goes in,

43
00:05:53,159 --> 00:05:53,960
you can...

44
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:57,220
Think about it.

45
00:05:57,840 --> 00:05:58,970
Sounds good, right?

46
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:01,640
Killing him yourself

47
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:04,000
is much more satisfying

48
00:06:04,440 --> 00:06:06,500
than sending him to prison, isn't it?

49
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,880
I've heard about it.

50
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:11,920
Xiao Tianman

51
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:15,560
pushed you out of Dayang Village back then,

52
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:20,800
leaving you alone and helpless in a strange place.

53
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:25,820
He took your business,

54
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,840
destroyed your family fortune,

55
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:33,720
and even played with your woman.

56
00:06:34,640 --> 00:06:36,800
He made you live like a dog.

57
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:41,810
You've thought about it, haven't you?

58
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:44,650
You've wanted revenge for a long time, right?

59
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,520
Enough.

60
00:06:53,840 --> 00:06:56,100
You want to kill two birds with one stone.

61
00:06:59,159 --> 00:07:00,020
President Gao,

62
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:04,280
I won't hurt you.

63
00:07:05,520 --> 00:07:08,250
If something happens to you, who will buy my gold?

64
00:07:08,320 --> 00:07:09,120
Really.

65
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,480
I just appreciate your help,

66
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:14,500
so I want to let you see how Xiao Tianman dies.

67
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:43,600
What's your plan?

68
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:09,880
Hello.

69
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:14,120
How have you been, Manager Xiao?

70
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:17,800
Who is this?

71
00:08:17,960 --> 00:08:18,890
What do you want?

72
00:08:20,640 --> 00:08:22,800
You couldn't have forgotten me so soon.

73
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,080
I'm Jiang Xiaomei.

74
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:25,770
Who did you say you were?

75
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,600
I'm Jiang Xiaomei.

76
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:30,920
Xiao Tianman.

77
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:33,880
I have evidence that you killed my parents.

78
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,440
What do you want?

79
00:08:40,400 --> 00:08:41,200
Where are you?

80
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,159
Want to know?

81
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:46,760
Come to Mine Shaft K26.

82
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:48,480
Let's have a chat.

83
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:59,330
What's wrong, Mr. Xiao?

84
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:01,480
Lao Er.

85
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:04,840
Do you know who just called?

86
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,160
Who?

87
00:09:06,920 --> 00:09:08,160
Jiang Xiaomei.

88
00:09:10,400 --> 00:09:11,640
Isn't she dead?

89
00:09:11,800 --> 00:09:13,080
How could she call?

90
00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:14,160
I want to know, too.

91
00:09:14,160 --> 00:09:15,680
Why is she still alive?

92
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:18,770
Impossible. Absolutely impossible.

93
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:20,400
I saw her dead with my own eyes.

94
00:09:20,400 --> 00:09:21,520
I saw it myself.

95
00:09:21,680 --> 00:09:22,840
There's no way she's alive.

96
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:24,640
She absolutely cannot be alive.

97
00:09:26,040 --> 00:09:27,720
Do you take me for a fool?

98
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:30,120
And easy to trick? No, Mr. Xiao.

99
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,120
No, Mr. Xiao.

100
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:34,080
Why is Jiang Xiaomei still alive?

101
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,600
Why is she alive?

102
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:37,200
I don't know. I saw her die.

103
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:37,920
And...

104
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:41,760
How on earth did Gao Shan know about my recorder?

105
00:09:41,760 --> 00:09:43,240
How did he know?

106
00:09:43,680 --> 00:09:44,920
I don't know anything.

107
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:46,760
I don't know anything, Mr. Xiao.

108
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:49,120
I really don't know.

109
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:57,280
Come with me

110
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:01,160
to see Jiang Xiaomei.

111
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:03,000
Let's go.

112
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:09,920
Yang Gang.

113
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:16,040
Yang Gang.

114
00:10:18,400 --> 00:10:19,200
Yang Gang.

115
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:24,760
Yang Gang.

116
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:38,720
Du Jing.

117
00:10:39,680 --> 00:10:40,480
Du Jing.

118
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:42,520
Look.

119
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:44,560
Look at this.

120
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:18,120
Xiaomei.
